{"tid":1299364,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲要號召抗爭？點解要特赦示威者？","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T19:48:44.000Z","uid":66390,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2eacdce4627787eee9d5657599199908a5300e49","tid":1299364,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等我話你知！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔講歷史 唔講點解以前香港特赦 呢家點解會違反法治精神啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>示威者因林鄭行政嚴重失誤而「違法」</ins></strong><br />\n林鄭都識講 修例工作<span style=\"color: red;\">完全失敗</span><br />\n係佢自己既施政失誤！<br />\n<br />\n因為你既施政失誤 示威者走上街頭<br />\n你可以話：雖然失誤 但無人叫你「違法」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果唔係激烈抗爭 無6.12 條條例通過左啦！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為你既失誤 而被捕</span><br />\n呢個邏輯上 仲唔應該<span style=\"color: red;\">為你既失敗而特赦？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">太陽花學運因為國民黨既施政失誤 而特赦「所有」被捕人士</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解唔可以特赦？</span> 此其一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其二！<strong><ins>堅持不成立獨立調查委員會 仍堅信監警會工作與功能</ins></strong><br />\n除左6.12  7.7警方濫權問題都係無法無天<br />\n諗下灰色衫個爛仔公安？<br />\nM記被打個個？點解記者唔可以入去？<span style=\"color: red;\">如何追究？</span><br />\n大家都見到陸續有人發信予監警會<br />\n但回覆係：無Number 處理唔到！7.7更明顯 全部除下編號 點追究？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我當你接受反送中條例啦<br />\n英文上：確有人以<strong>The Bill is Dead 表示撤回</strong><br />\n英文上可能說得過去<br />\n但<strong>受終正寢</strong>更能表示條例係<span style=\"color: red;\">正在休息</span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭又話 就算用「撤回」兩個字<br />\n一樣可以重提！<br />\n我又當你既邏輯上無分別啦<br />\n但呢家就係大眾條氣好唔撚順 係要堅持「撤回」<br />\n唔可以為左修補社會裂痕而用「撤回」？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">條例既抗爭號召力可能因而減低 但黑警與義士問題未結</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅持追究黑警責任 成立獨立調查委員會</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特赦被捕示威者 拯救義士</span></span><br />\n<br />\n抗爭必須繼續<br />\n香港沒有休息的一天<br />\n13/7 上水見"},{"pid":"0e1bb759a9ffdf19e7f81c6684ae55fdcb7e1c0c","tid":1299364,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5a2639f72e8d7b6f14c567dfdfeaaf50391c7e","tid":1299364,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKzEh69.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKzEh69.png&h=ed5fc722&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"160c3ba2b7f443016a549fa8c2aa0261c1f68a30","tid":1299364,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究黑警責任 成立獨立調查委員會</span></span>"},{"pid":"331917dc3f1f3f351cf0a28fd2e56415bc821b20","tid":1299364,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:54:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特赦示威者 拯救義士</span></span>"},{"pid":"26f26b34921e9bdeca02c3417e20afe58b20dc6d","tid":1299364,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535d67aca146637861fef90440bd616ad0acc481","tid":1299364,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8245ca465ec04cb161c832a61f0a43d643b86e3d","tid":1299364,"uid":66390,"like"